 \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are an inspiration for women and girls everywhere.\\\"\", \"from\": 5999, \"to\": 6054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LATEST SPORTS NEWS:  A post shared by Imane Khelif | \\u0625\\u064a\\u0645\\u0627\\u0646 \\u062e\\u0644\\u064a\\u0641 \\ud83c\\udde9\\ud83c\\uddff (@imane_khelif_10)  It is currently unclear what the future holds for Khelif following her gold medal.\", \"from\": 6056, \"to\": 6225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6096, \"end\": 6108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But boxing promoter Eddie Hearn, speaking earlier this week, said he was open to giving the 25-year-old a professional contract.\", \"from\": 6227, \"to\": 6355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6235, \"end\": 6250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Promoter_(entertainment)\", \"score\": 0.9999998352591455, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"boxing promoter\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Promoter_(entertainment)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Promoter_(entertainment)\"}, {\"begin\": 6251, \"end\": 6262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eddie_Hearn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.943578694204201e-37, \"text\": \"Eddie Hearn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eddie_Hearn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eddie_Hearn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, if the facts were laid out and it was in a position where there is no reason why this individual should not compete as a female,\\\" he told IFL TV when asked if that was possible.\", \"from\": 6357, \"to\": 6540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6505, \"end\": 6508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Fight_League\", \"score\": 0.9999646287272577, \"rank\": 3.535947825236634e-05, \"text\": \"IFL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Fight_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Fight_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, I would, commercially.\", \"from\": 6542, \"to\": 6570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One, she is a talented fighter.\", \"from\": 6571, \"to\": 6602, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two, commercially I think she has up to two Instagram million followers, up from 30,000, so the answer is yes.\", \"from\": 6603, \"to\": 6713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Imane Khelif was given a hero's welcome by the people of Algeria after her gold medal triumph at the Paris Olympics  GETTY  \\\"But there is probably facts that we do not know are true around the situation.\", \"from\": 6715, \"to\": 6918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6719, \"end\": 6731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 6776, \"end\": 6783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999999981610017, \"rank\": 1.8338757334993554e-09, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But if a fighter was deemed, you know, female with no physical advantages, but again we hear about X/Y chromosomes, and I have not seen anything, I have just seen someone say: 'We have done this test.'\", \"from\": 6920, \"to\": 7122, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Do we get to see it?\", \"from\": 7124, \"to\": 7145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Or are we just going to believe that narrative?\", \"from\": 7146, \"to\": 7193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not ever one that I'd ever go: 'I am not getting involved in this conversation.\", \"from\": 7195, \"to\": 7280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a topical conversation.'\\\"\", \"from\": 7281, \"to\": 7311, \"entities\": []}]}"